Description: The major goal of ggtranscript is the simplify the process of 
    visualizing transcript structure and annotation. ggtranscript achieves by 
    introducing 4 geoms (geom_range, geom_half_range, geom_intron and
    geom_junction) and several helper functions that are designed to visualize 
    transcript annotation using ggplot2. As a ggplot2 extension, ggtranscript 
    inherits ggplot2's familiarity and flexibility; users can intuitively adjust 
    aesthetics and parameters as well as complement ggtranscript geoms with 
    existing ggplot2 geoms. 
